'''Tormented demons''' are extremely powerful [[demons]] bound into a state of perpetual agony, healing their bodies as they burn, summoned by the [[Mahjarrat]] [[Lucien]] after he teleports away the [[Stone of Jas]] during [[While Guthix Sleeps]]. They can be found throughout the [[Ancient Guthixian Temple]] after completion of the quest.

Tormented demons count as [[greater demons]] for the progression of [[Slayer task]]s. As demons, they are susceptible to the effects of [[demonbane weapons]].

They are primarily killed for their [[tormented synapse]]s, which are used to create high-tier demonbane weapons, as well as their [[burning claw]] drop, two of which are combined into the [[burning claws]], a [[special attack]] weapon that sits in between the [[dragon dagger]] and [[dragon claws]] in terms of power.

